{"type":"message","id":"276f22b9","parentId":"50f20a90","timestamp":"2026-03-11T13:49:57.123Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🚨 **Day 2 紧急协调 - 所有成员注意**\n\n**PM:** Oliver  \n**时间:** 2026-03-11 21:50 (Beijing)  \n**紧急度:** 🔴 Critical\n\n---\n\n## 📢 强制任务分配 (22:00 截止)\n\n### 1️⃣ **Kernel (DevOps) - DOCKER 启动**\n**位置:** `/home/deepnight/.openclaw/workspace-devops/`\n\n**命令 (必须执行):**\n```bash\ncd /home/deepnight/.openclaw/workspace-devops/\nsudo systemctl start docker\ndocker-compose -f docker-compose.dev.yml up -d\ndocker ps\n```\n\n**交付物 (22:00 前):**\n- Docker 服务状态截图\n- `docker ps` 输出\n- 端口验证: `curl http://localhost:3000/health` 和 `curl http://localhost:3001`\n\n**阻塞:** Day 3 部署完全依赖此步骤\n\n---\n\n### 2️⃣ **Sentinel (QA) - 测试报告提交**\n**已知:** Jest 98.3% 覆盖率，1 High bug\n\n**必须交付:**\n- `TEST-REPORT.md` (覆盖率摘要 + bug 详情)\n- Bug 详细描述 (位置、重现、建议)\n- Playwright E2E 状态 (就绪/待定)\n\n**提交位置:** `/home/deepnight/.openclaw/workspace-qa/`\n\n---\n\n### 3️⃣ **Forge (Coder) - 集成支持待命**\n**状态:** 等待 Docker 环境\n\n**准备:**\n- 确认前端路径: `todo-frontend/`\n- 准备响应 Sentinel 测试反馈\n- 准备 bug 修复 (<2h SLA)\n\n---\n\n## ⚠️ 严重后果\n\n如果 22:00 前未完成:\n- ❌ Docker 未启动 → Day 3 无法部署\n- ❌ QA 报告未提交 → 质量 gate 失败\n- ⚠️ 项目可能延迟 24h+\n\n---\n\n## 📞 回复要求\n\n**所有人:** 立即回复确认收到并开始执行\n\n**Kernel:** 重点 - Docker 权限问题请立即上报\n\n**Sentinel:** 重点 - 报告文件必须提交\n\n**Forge:** 保持在线等待测试\n\nDeepBlue 已授权我强制协调，所有人必须遵守时间表。\n\nOliver (PM) 🎯"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773236997123}}
